**DRAFT**

Setting up the AppServer

You need to run the following command to generate a config file:

$ paster make-config appserver appserver_production.ini

You need to edit the config file for your production environment with the settings you want and then run this command
to setup the application:

$ paster setup-app appserver_production.ini

You can then deploy the AppServer through the paste server like this:

$ paster serve appserver_production.ini
